{"id":7495,"date":"2021-10-09T22:10:48","date_gmt":"2021-10-09T15:10:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=7495"},"modified":"2023-11-22T12:46:57","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T05:46:57","slug":"bat-dong-san-tieng-anh-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/bat-dong-san-tieng-anh-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi nghe \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb \u201c<strong>B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/strong>\u201d, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng ai c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng ngay \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai. C\u00e1ch ngh\u0129 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 sai, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf trong ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a \u201cb\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\u201d.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7496\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7496\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7496 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/chu-ky-bat-dong-san-la-gi-min.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh\" width=\"800\" height=\"603\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/603;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7496\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7496\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/chu-ky-bat-dong-san-la-gi-min.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh\" width=\"800\" height=\"603\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7496\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin, hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 n\u00e0y. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> s\u1ebd th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 \u201c b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec \u201d m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Vinhomes Grand Park<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i t\u00ean g\u1ecdi b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, th\u00ec nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t hay \u0111\u1ecba \u1ed1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u00fd ngh\u0129a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt. D\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1ch r\u1eddi v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1ecfi m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, chung c\u01b0, nh\u00e0 \u1edf, d\u00e0n khoan d\u1ea7u kh\u00ed hay d\u1ea7u m\u1ecf d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5t,\u2026 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean v\u00e0 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n v\u1edbi m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t. C\u00f2n nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 t\u00e1ch r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 l\u1ec1u, nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1m b\u1ee3, nh\u00e0 di \u0111\u1ed9ng,\u2026<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7497\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7497\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7497 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/bds-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"521\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/521;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7497\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7497\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/bds-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"521\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7497\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua, cho thu\u00ea, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i di ch\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u1eb7c v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kinh doanh, b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kinh doanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u1ea5t cao. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong t\u1eebng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 thu h\u00fat nh\u1eefng N\u0110T m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m l\u00e0m gi\u00e0u. Mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u doanh thu v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn to l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi N\u0110T n\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u00ea\u0301ng Anh la\u0300 gi\u0300<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ti\u1ebfng Anh, b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch th\u00e0nh \u201creal property\u201d hay \u201creal estate\u201d. L\u00e0 c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u201cpersonal property\u201d.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7498\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7498\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7498 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-7.jpg\" alt=\"B\u0110S Ti\u1ebfng Anh \" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/533;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7498\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7498\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-7.jpg\" alt=\"B\u0110S Ti\u1ebfng Anh \" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7498\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u0110S Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cPersonal property\u201d v\u00e0 \u201cReal estate\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng theo nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p. Theo \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n n\u1eb1m trong \u201cb\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\u201d lu\u00f4n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai. Khi chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u201c\u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\u201d th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0, m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u0103n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u2013 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, trang tr\u00ed b\u00ean trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u0103n nh\u00e0 \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb th\u1eddi phong ki\u1ebfn t\u01b0 b\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ee7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 coi tr\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef \u201cb\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\u201d ra \u0111\u1eddi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1660.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7499 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/bat-dong-san-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"509\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/509;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7499\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/bat-dong-san-la-gi.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"509\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0129nh v\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n th\u00e0nh 3 nh\u00f3m ch\u00ednh:<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t: bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean n\u00f3, g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p r\u1ed1i r\u1eafm cao, mang t\u1ef7 tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c B\u0110S.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ B\u0110S nh\u00e0 x\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ B\u0110S h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ B\u0110S tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c,\u2026<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a qua s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm, \u0111\u1ea5t d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m mu\u1ed1i, nu\u00f4i tr\u1ed3ng th\u1ee7y h\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n,\u00a0 d\u00f9ng cho n\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p\u2026<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7500 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/quy-dinh-ve-su-dung-dat-co-mat-nuoc-de-nuoi-trong-thuy-san.jpeg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"477\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/477;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7500\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/quy-dinh-ve-su-dung-dat-co-mat-nuoc-de-nuoi-trong-thuy-san.jpeg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"477\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1n ch\u00f9a, ngh\u0129a trang, khu di t\u00edch, b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n qu\u1ed1c gia, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac v\u0103n ho\u00e1,\u2026<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Grand Marina Saigon<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, B\u0110S l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn. \u0110\u01b0a v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kinh doanh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh. Kinh doanh B\u0110S nh\u1eb1m ch\u1ec9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ngu\u1ed3n v\u1ed1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trao \u0111\u1ed5i, mua b\u00e1n, cho thu\u00ea, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi B\u0110S.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7501\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7501\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7501 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/530;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7501\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7501\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/unnamed-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7501\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 mua b\u00e1n B\u0110S. C\u00e1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, giao d\u1ecbch, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch, doanh thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c, l\u1ee3i l\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng mua b\u00e1n v\u00e0 kinh doanh. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, ngu\u1ed3n v\u1ed1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, t\u00edch c\u00f3p v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n B\u0110S, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, cho thu\u00ea, mua \u0111i b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch sinh l\u1eddi, thu l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f4i gi\u1edbi b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7504 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dau-tu-bat-dong-san-kyna-2.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"511\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/511;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7504\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dau-tu-bat-dong-san-kyna-2.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"511\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u1edf trung gian, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean tham gia mua b\u00e1n, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng B\u0110S.<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ Nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda, c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n<\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda, c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1eb5n, chung c\u01b0,\u2026.<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\">+ Nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda, c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai<\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi c\u00f4ng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7503 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dau-tu-bat-dong-san-doanhnhansaigon-1508433903.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"523\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/523;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7503\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dau-tu-bat-dong-san-doanhnhansaigon-1508433903.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"523\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi B\u0110S, khai th\u00e1c theo u\u1ef7 quy\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e0n giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec\u00a0<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng giao d\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, cho thu\u00ea, mua b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u00ec<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn, tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u00ean tham gia mua b\u00e1n, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, cho thu\u00ea v\u1ec1 B\u0110S li\u00ean quan.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bong b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec\u00a0<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng mua b\u00e1n hay kinh doanh, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n g\u00ec c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 khi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Trong B\u0110S c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 B\u0110S. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nghe qua c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb \u201cbong b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n\u201d.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7502\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7502\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7502 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/29205914-2-bong-bong-bat-dong-san.jpg\" alt=\"Bong b\u00f3ng B\u0110S\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/480;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7502\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7502\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/29205914-2-bong-bong-bat-dong-san.jpg\" alt=\"Bong b\u00f3ng B\u0110S\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-7502\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bong b\u00f3ng B\u0110S<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef nh\u1eb1m bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n t\u0103ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u1ea3o. N\u1ebfu bong b\u00f3ng th\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 c\u0103ng so v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c th\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd v\u1ee1.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u0110S c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, khi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u1ecfi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc cho ph\u00e9p s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ecb ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng n\u1eefa v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ee5t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng phanh, khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng B\u0110S s\u1ebd b\u1ecb v\u1ee1.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\"><strong>vinhomeland.com.vn<\/strong><\/a>, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1<strong> B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/strong> c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00ean ti\u1ebfng anh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m, nh\u1eefng quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a B\u0110S. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;7495&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ti\u1ebfng Anh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<d